{"metadata":{"title":"TokensProvider Implementations","roleHeading":"API Collection","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"role":"collectionGroup"},"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider\/tokensprovider-implementations"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"title":"Instance Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider\/checkInstances(count:for:)"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods","generated":true}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider/checkInstances(count:for:)":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider\/checkinstances(count:for:)","title":"checkInstances(count:for:)","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"checkInstances"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"count"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"for"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider\/checkInstances(count:for:)","kind":"symbol","abstract":[]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of alert"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"alert"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSAlert","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllAlertComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"AlertComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"alert"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Alert"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of borders ("},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProviders","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") and sizes (from "},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"title":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","kind":"symbol"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","title":"Theme Orange"}}}